creator: QRTAG aplikacje mobilne, programy lojalnościowe
descriptionHtml:
“The app SIGN WITH US: PJM is the perfect tool to spread knowledge of Polish sign language (polski język migowy, PJM) and to facilitate the communication between hearing people and Deaf people using PJM. It allows anybody to learn the basics of PJM or to further develop their skills.
The app contains over 150 videos with the alphabet, signs and expressions”.
